      <Content>In a number of contexts, ἐπιβλέπω involves not only sight but a considerable focus upon an accompanying mental activity, so that one may classify ἐπιβλέπω not only as meaning sight but as indicating paying attention to or even concerning oneself with (see {D:30.45}).</Content>
